spirit:component.spirit:description: I2S Transmitter can be used to output PCM data to external CODECs for Audio playback. It can output upto 8 channels of PCM data. The IP supports Audio sample size of 16 or 24.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: C_DWIDTH
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: This is the width of valid data sample. Possible values are 16 and 24.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: C_32BIT_LR
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Select this to enable I2S transmit the data with 32 bit SCLK. Valid sample bits is determined by the data width selected
